; Output: LOOPS_MACRO.M
; Console: LOOPS_MACRO.OUT

#Title LOOPS_MACRO
#Filename LOOPS_MACRO.M
#Option /v/c

; Exercise repeats, alternate endings, ties, slurs

; Part A: simple nested repeat and tie
A t120 o4 l8 [cdef]2 a4
A c8d8e8f8 c2&c2

; Part B: simple ties and dotted lengths
B l4 c c&c d d&d e2 f.

; Part C: long repeat
C l16 [cdefgabc]2

; Part D: note length modifiers and dotted notes
D l8 c. d.. e1... f2&f4

; Part E: change default length mid-stream
E l4 c d l8 e f l16 g a l8 b>c<

; Rhythm hint via rests and spacing
R0 l8 r r r r
R1 l8 r r r r
K R0 R1
